\begin{comment}
The title of my lecture is "The fortress at the end of the world" 
and I want to do two things. The first is to introduce you to the site 
of Zawiyet Umm el-Rakham and try to explain its historical and 
geographical context. The second is to discuss various types of 
evidence from the site which can help us to understand how the 
population of this fortress lived including the relationship of its 
inhabitants with the local population. 
\end{comment}

